data.description: What an AWESOME opportunity to own a beautiful 4 SIDE BRICK RANCH home on almost an Acre lot! This spacious floorplan boast 2300 sq ft. Once you walk into the foyer, you'll fall in love with all the customary features this home has to offer. Features include hardwood flooring in foyer, large eat in kitchen with bay window, SS appliances, breakfast bar, step-down family room with fireplace, bonus area/office, spacious master bedroom features 2 walk-in closets and dual vanity in bathroom. For your outdoor enjoyment is a nice patio for grilling, level backyard, large shed near the back of yard; ideal for a workshop or simply additional storage, 2 car side entry carport and an extended driveway. Plenty of space for additional parking, boat or RV. Very private community located in superb school district. With an OPTIONAL HOA, you can enjoy community events or a simple walk around the tranquil lake. Membership to the community also allows access to swim/tennis/social club. This home is a MUST SEE!
